-- Bank of Cyprus Chairman Artemis submits resignation: source
-- 
-- Tue Mar 26, 2013 7:06am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/03/26/us-eurozone-cyprus-artemis-idUSBRE92P0EE20130326

 

 NICOSIA  (Reuters) - Andreas Artemis, the chairman of Cyprus's biggest commercial bank, the Bank of Cyprus, has submitted his resignation, a source at the bank said on Tuesday. 
 "He sent a resignation letter this morning which will be examined by the Board of Directors convening this afternoon," the bank source said, requesting anonymity. (Reporting by  Michele Kambas ; Writing by  Giles Elgood )